sequenceDiagram
    participant Frontend as Frontend
    participant Auth as Auth
    participant Backend as Backend

    Frontend->>Auth: /oauth/authorize + code_challenge (S256)
    Auth->>Frontend: auth code
    Frontend->>Auth: /oauth/token + code_verifier
    Note over Auth: SHA256(verifier) == challenge ✓
    Auth->>Frontend: access_token (JWT)
    Frontend->>Backend: Bearer JWT
    Backend->>Auth: GET /api/user (Bearer JWT)
    Auth->>Backend: { id, name, email, ... }
    Note over Backend: active → grant access
    Backend->>Frontend: protected resource
